to check whether you have added the right index on the posts collection, run
 python validate.py
You don't need to have the blog running for validate to succeed. 
You might want to look at the blog code to see what queries it does to the posts collection. they need
to be fast.

Manifest:

stuff to run the blog:
 blog.py
 user.py 
 views/*.tpl

data that needs to be imported:
 posts.json

validationscript:
 validate.py
 
